# 4. Register service in `Program.cs`

```csharp
using Microsoft.AspNetCore.Http.Features;
using TodoApi.Services;

var maxUploadSize = 50L * 1024L * 1024L; // 50 MB per chunk

builder.Services.Configure<FormOptions>(options =>
{
    options.MultipartBodyLengthLimit = maxUploadSize;
});

builder.WebHost.ConfigureKestrel(options =>
{
    options.Limits.MaxRequestBodySize = maxUploadSize;
});

builder.Services.AddScoped<OnPremChunkUploadService>();
```

Important: with chunk upload, this limit is **per chunk**, not the full file.

Example:

```text
Chunk size = 10 MB
Max request size = 50 MB
Final file can be 10 GB+
```

